<h1 id="about-dragonz">About Dragonz</h1>
<p>Dragonz introduces us to Flint, Frost, Switch and Gobble four small yet mighty dragons. The slot is played on the standard five reels with five lines but it has no less than 243 ways to win. As for features the game has four different free spin rounds and the Wild Deal feature.</p>
<h2 id="game-features">Game features</h2>
<p>The main feature in Dragonz is the Free Spins. Each dragon has his own Free Spin round. Triggering the Free Spins bonus 12 times unlocks the Player Choice reward where players select which Free Spin feature they want to play. The second feature in Dragonz, the Wild Deal activates when a non winning wild lands on the third reel.</p>
<h3 id="free-spins">Free Spins</h3>
<p>Free Spins are activated by getting three Scatter symbols anywhere on the reels. The last bet placed is used all through the Free Spins. Also worth mentioning is that there is no way of winning additional Free Spins during the free spin rounds.</p>
<h4 id="flint-free-spins">Flint Free Spins</h4>
<ul>
<li>Flaming Wilds are active during these Free Spins.</li>
<li>An increasing number of wilds get scattered on each spin while these are active.</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="switch-free-spins">Switch Free Spins</h4>
<ul>
<li>Stashed Wilds are active during these Free Spins. Meaning all non-winning symbols are stashed.</li>
<li>If three or more wild symbols are stashed they get randomly scattered, creating a winning combination.</li>
<li>The Free Spins continue until all stashed wilds have been awarded.</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="frost-free-spins">Frost Free Spins</h4>
<ul>
<li>These Free Spins has the Frosty Wilds feature. This means all wild symbols are frozen in place until they are part of a winning combination.</li>
<li>Free Spins will continue as long as there are frozen wilds on the reels.</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="gobble-free-spins">Gobble Free Spins</h4>
<ul>
<li>Winning Wilds is the feature active during these Free Spins. Extra wilds are scattered on the reels and remain in place until they’re no longer part of a winning combination.</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="wild-deal">Wild Deal</h3>
<p>When a non-winning wild lands on the third reel this feature activates, randomly placing wilds on the reels, guaranteeing a win.</p>
<h2 id="game-details">Game details</h2>
<ul>
<li>Developer: <a href="http://www.microgaming.co.uk">Microgaming</a></li>
<li>Reels &amp; lines: 5 reels, 3 rows, 243 bet lines</li>
<li>Bet levels: 1-15</li>
